CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1784209690
OL,3,CStones' boyhood coach says his
OL,4,C'experience' could be key against Messi
OL,6,FMessi's eight goals in the tournament
OL,7,Fso far put him joint top in the race
OL,8,Ffor the golden boot - the award for
OL,9,Fthe World Cup's most prolific marksman.
OL,11,FRemarkably, in a career spanning more
OL,12,Fthan two decades, his appearance
OL,13,Fagainst England on Wednesday will be
OL,14,Fhis first against the Three Lions.
OL,16,FBut thousands of miles from the Deep
OL,17,FSouth there's confidence that a lad
OL,18,Ffrom South Yorkshire could hold the
OL,19,Fkey to neutralising the Messi threat.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1784209690
OL,3,CStones' boyhood coach says his
OL,4,C'experience' could be key against Messi
OL,6,FMark Burton was head of academy
OL,7,Fcoaching at Barnsley between 2007 and
OL,8,F2017 and worked with defender John
OL,9,FStones as he rose through the ranks at
OL,10,FOakwell.
OL,12,FStones played 28 times for his
OL,13,Fhometown club before moving to Everton
OL,14,Fand later Manchester City.
OL,16,FBurton said: "I think Stones'
OL,17,Fexperience is needed in a game like
OL,18,Fthis. He understands what's needed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1784209690
OL,3,CStones' boyhood coach says his
OL,4,C'experience' could be key against Messi
OL,6,F"But, we can't get too focused on
OL,7,FLionel Messi's the best player in the
OL,8,Fworld, they have other good players
OL,9,Faround them.
OL,11,F"Every time he gets on the ball,
OL,12,Fyou've got to be looking at runners,
OL,13,Fyou've got to look at McAllister and
OL,14,FAlvarez."
OL,16,FThe South Americans have won all six
OL,17,Fof their matches so far, but have
OL,18,Fridden their luck at times.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1784209690
OL,3,CStones' boyhood coach says his
OL,4,C'experience' could be key against Messi
OL,6,FThey needed extra time to beat World
OL,7,FCup debutants Cape Verde and had to
OL,8,Fcome back from two goals down to
OL,9,Fovercome Egypt in the last 16.
OL,11,FBurton said: "Argentina have got their
OL,12,Fvulnerabilities. They are really
OL,13,Fexpansive and if England play the way
OL,14,Fthat we can, communicate well with
OL,15,Feach other, and break quickly, I think
OL,16,Fthere's goals."
OL,18,FThe coach said he feels an immense
OL,19,Fsense of pride when John Stones plays
OL,20,Ffor England.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1784209690
OL,3,CStones' boyhood coach says his
OL,4,C'experience' could be key against Messi
OL,6,FHe added: "We always want England to
OL,7,Fwin something in our lifetime, and
OL,8,Fwhen you've got a player who you've
OL,9,Fhad, a big part of the journey of that
OL,10,Fgives a sort of edge when you're
OL,11,Fwatching him on the television in a
OL,12,FWorld Cup quarterfinal, your heart's
OL,13,Fin your mouth.
OL,15,F"If he's successful with the team,
OL,16,Fthere'll be no prouder man in Barnsley
OL,17,Fthan me."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
