PN,33307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1784209690
OL,3,CStones' boyhood coach says his
OL,4,C'experience' could be key against Messi
OL,6,FAnother Yorkshireman with experience
OL,7,Fagainst Argentina is former England
OL,8,FGoalkeeper David Seaman, from
OL,9,FRotherham, who played in two World Cup
OL,10,Fgames against the South American
OL,11,Foutfit in 1998 and 2002.
OL,13,FHe believes that, as in 2002 when
OL,14,FEngland won 1-0 thanks to a David
OL,15,FBeckham penalty, Stones and co will
OL,16,Fkeep Argentina at bay. He said:
OL,17,F"They've got a chance.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
