FL,334,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F333A1784209690
OL,3,CStones' boyhood coach says his
OL,4,C'experience' could be key against Messi
OL,6,F"It's about England playing as a team,
OL,7,Fyou know, obviously they've got a an
OL,8,Funbelievable player in their squad,
OL,9,Fbut you know I still feel that if we
OL,10,Fplay our best, we win."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
